Huwág kayóng mag-away kasí pwede namáng mapag-usapan iyán nang maayos.	Don't quarrel because that is something that may be settled amicably by talking
Huwág kayóng mag-away kasí pwede namáng mapag-usapan iyán nang maayos. 	Don't quarrel because that is something that may be settled amicably by talking
